- "What C++ class is this vtable?" â†’ `rtti.py vtable` (see RTTI notes below)
- "What type was a caught/thrown exception?" â†’ `rtti.py throwinfo` (see RTTI notes below)
- "What DLL functions are exported?" â†’ `search.py exports`
- "Find all instructions using a specific constant" â†’ `search.py insn`
